{"tid":1968711,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[白宮聯署]最後一日，望吓個堆人名你忍得住唔簽？","createTime":"2020-04-12T01:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T14:53:43.000Z","uid":337613,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ce63777f8f10418d0b7f9fa5a6511cbbf6195180","tid":1968711,"uid":337613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T01:06:51.000Z","msg":"又係得番一日，差二萬八千個簽署&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n望吓個堆人名，無理由忍得住唔簽<br />\n如果簽咗幫手share去同溫層以外地方🙇🏻&zwj;♂️🙇🏻&zwj;♂️🙇🏻&zwj;♂️🙇🏻&zwj;♂️🙇🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\n以下為該聯署既翻譯： <br />\n<br />\n香港人希望美國根據人權法，在制裁名單中增加以下立法會議員：李慧琼、周浩鼎、梁美芬、葉劉淑儀、葛珮帆、何君堯、何啟明、陳健波、蔣麗雲。<br />\n<br />\n他們盲目支持中國政府，甚至支持林鄭月娥於2019年6月推行送中條例，以致社會及全球經濟動盪。他們在香港人心中是危險的人，因為他們同意林鄭月娥通過惡法。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我們要求將上述人員納入制裁範圍，並且不再讓他們進入美國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-add-new-sanctions-list-hk-human-rights-law-starry-lee-holden-chow-dr-priscilla-leung-ms-regina-ip-etc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-add-new-sanctions-list-hk-human-rights-law-starry-lee-holden-chow-dr-priscilla-leung-ms-regina-ip-etc&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=2709c802\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-add-new-sanctions-list-hk-human-rights-law-starry-lee-holden-chow-dr-priscilla-leung-ms-regina-ip-etc</a>"},{"pid":"19e415bba9dc8e412349c73ca97b6e509583f86d","tid":1968711,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T01:12:09.000Z","msg":"大家未簽就簽<br />\n簽左就share出去"},{"pid":"47b891b0a76613c857558d5e9ffb0c2276140a2f","tid":1968711,"uid":339091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T02:50:48.000Z","msg":"推呀推呀!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c8750f89579c89bf792e6d49547dd0ae5de70